title: Jami Morgan from Code Orange
itunes:title: Jami Morgan from Code Orange
description:
Making history as being the youngest guest on the show, drummer/vocalist Jami Morgan from Code Orange is on the show today. He and I had a great chat one afternoon about embarrassing first bands, depression and being the "business man" of the band.
